: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(71, 69, 69); font-size: 18px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">山西报国寺《不忘初心智慧营》是多年来，十方信众各界精英期盼，迟迟而来的智慧之光，是我们和谐社会不可或缺的音符，在非常有限的七天时间，将为学员和义工举行礼佛、诵经、过堂、禅修、观影、茶道、传灯、梵呗音乐等系列丰富体验活动。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(71, 69, 69); font-size: 18px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><br/></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(71, 69, 69); font-size: 18px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">活动期间由专人陪护，法师引导，让我们全息进入宗教文化体验，沐浴佛恩之中，让心灵点燃智慧之光，感悟知恩报恩，人生在于奉献的价值源泉！让我们一起巡礼佛教丛林生活，依止修行者问道，感受圣教，自由源于持戒，戒律才是身心解放的究竟保障！</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><img title="14944031849993.jpg" alt="报国寺 1.jpg" src="/upload/images/201705/14944031849993.jpg"/></p><p style="padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px;"><span style="font-size: 18px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(88, 46, 46); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="font-size: 15px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(88, 46, 46); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"></span></strong></span>本寺院历来接受国家政府监督，为报众生恩，行愿佛陀慈悲济世布施法露，今志愿服务社会公民，鼓励青年踊跃参与，身体健康者均有机会参加，让我们做一个有益于社会的人，做一个有价值的人，做一个有意义的人，做一个和谐社会的使者。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">本次《不忘初心智慧营》活动，年龄限制在18-40岁之间，名额非常有限，学员限招60人，义工限招30人，满员即止，以录取通知书为准。<br/></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><img src="/upload/images/201705/14950323447732.jpg" title="14950323447732.jpg" alt="IMG_3238.JPG" style="color: rgb(71, 69, 69); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; white-space: normal;"/></p><p style="padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(71, 69, 69); font-size: 18px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">山西报国寺位于盂县县城东北五公里处，环境优美，灵气十足，相传后周皇帝年幼，契丹入侵，朝廷派赵匡胤北上御敌。不料，中途发生“陈桥兵变”赵匡胤皇袍加身，取后周而代之，周世宗之女柴花公主从小性情刚烈，不甘身委于赵宋，连夜逃走，来至水神山屈居多年，后觉复国无望，而自尽于水神山抱泉楼侧一棵枣树上。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(71, 69, 69); font-size: 18px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px; color: rgb(71, 69, 69);">因柴花公主同情怜悯劳苦大众，尽心慧施本地百姓，死后一方民众为了缅怀纪念这位义女就地而建“后周圣母祠”几乎完整留存至今！<br/></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><img title="14944026555512.jpg" alt="报国寺 3.jpg" src="/upload/images/201705/14944026555512.jpg"/></p><p style="padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">如今，十方信众，一方百姓为纪念这位可歌可泣的忠烈女子，纷纷捐钱、捐物建寺纪念。2011年，盂县佛教协会为弘扬水神山烈女忠义精神，再现后周文化的情韵，重新修复报国寺。</span></p><p style="padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="font-size: 18px;">新建的报国寺占地面积120亩。寺内建有观音殿、天王殿、大文殊殿、法堂、文化研究书院等场所。&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 18px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(71, 69, 69); max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"></span></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -ms-word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(71, 69, 69); font-size: 18px; max-width: 100% !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;"><img src="/upload/images/201705/14950301274400.jpg" title="14950301274400.jpg" alt="报国寺 5_meitu_1.jpg"/></span></p><p style="padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em; clear: both; margin-top: 15px; margin-bottom: 15px; -m